        {
            "id": 6011237,
            "title": "川普、馬斯克翻臉！WSJ：川普考慮賣掉紅色特斯拉",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據《華爾街日報》（WSJ）報導，白宮一位高階官員透露，川普總統正在考慮出售或贈送今年年初購買的紅色特斯拉 (<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSLA\">TSLA-US</a>) 。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011237%2Fl%2Fa3f23edf6dbefad6c96f86b53ba66e0e.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">白宮一位高階官員透露，川普總統正在考慮出售或贈送今年年初購買的紅色特斯拉 。（圖：Shutterstock）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>當初川普買下這輛電動車，是為了幫特斯拉執行長馬斯克做宣傳。截至周四（5 日）晚間，那輛特斯拉仍停在白宮西翼外。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普周五受訪時表示：「我不打算和他通話，祝他好運吧。」他接著說：「我現在根本沒在想馬斯克，他有問題，這可憐的傢伙有問題。」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>這場風波起因於馬斯克批評川普政府的稅改法案，稱該法案可能進一步推高美國債務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普在白宮橢圓形辦公室對馬斯克大加抨擊，甚至威脅切斷 SpaceX 等相關聯邦合約。馬斯克隨即在社群平台 X 上回擊，稱川普「忘恩負義」，並直言如果沒有他大手筆捐款，川普根本不可能打贏總統選戰。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
